(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Acids.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind properties of acids and) Tj
T*
(reactions with metals, bases, and carbonates.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct chemical reasoning process step by step instead of jumping to the) Tj
T*
(answer.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the result carefully and confirm that it matches the requirement of the topic.) Tj
