T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on predicting products when an acid reacts with a metal.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in properties of acids and reactions with metals, bases, and) Tj
T*
(carbonates that the question is testing.) Tj
